---
---

<section id="about" class="relative px-6 py-32 bg-slate-800/50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 inline-block relative">
        About Me
        <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full animate-gradient-x"></div>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="relative group">
      <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/30 via-purple-500/30 to-blue-500/30 rounded-3xl blur-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
      <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-700/70 to-slate-800/70 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-600/50 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
            I'm a dedicated Full Stack Developer based in Kathmandu, Nepal, with a passion for building innovative software solutions. My journey in technology began with a curiosity about how things work, and has evolved into a career focused on creating impactful applications.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
            With experience spanning multiple roles at Corbig Technology Pvt. Ltd., I've developed expertise in modern web development technologies and agile methodologies. I thrive in collaborative environments where I can contribute to meaningful projects while continuously learning and growing.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
            Whether working independently or as part of a team, I'm committed to delivering high-quality code and user experiences that make a difference.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-slate-600/50">
          <div class="text-center group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 mb-2 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              4+
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-400 text-sm group-hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors">Years Experience</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-blue-400 mb-2 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              20+
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-400 text-sm group-hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors">Projects Completed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 mb-2 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              3
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-400 text-sm group-hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors">Companies</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
